  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>You can enjoy a stress-free holiday when staying in one of these Ylläsrinne cabins as the cabins include a half-board basis, with breakfast and dinner enjoyed at the Ylläsrinne Hotel. </p>
<p>You'll also have the option to have lunch included at the Ylläsrinne Hotel for an extra supplement.</p>
<p>A Festive Feast is included for all guests staying in these cabins for winter 2023.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
