  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p>The cabins are within walking distance of the Ylläsrinne Hotel where your half board meals will be taken. it is between 150 - 1,000 metres walk depending on the cabin you are staying in.</p>
<p>It is 3.5 kilometres to Ylläsjarvi Ski Resort from the cabins and there is a ski bus service which you can pay for locally.</p>
<p>It is also 14 kilometres to <span>Äkäslompolo town located on the other side of the fell with a bus service connecting the two sides.</span></p>]]></locationDescription>
