  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p>We've handpicked these 13 cabins for their unique charm and furnishings. Scattered in the grounds surrounding the Ylläsrinne Hotel, they range from 150 to 1000 metres away from the hotel. Each property is equipped with Wi-Fi and firewood is provided as standard. </p>
<p>As a minimum, all cabins provide kitchen facilities with fridge, oven, microwave, kettle and toaster. They all have a sauna to warm up in after exploring the great outdoors, plus one linen and towel set is included, per person per week. </p>
<p>Please note that the steps to the mezzanines are steep and mezzanine ceilings are low or sloping. </p>
<p><strong>Kissalanminttu 1</strong>,<strong> 2, 3 &amp; 4 </strong>sleep 1-4 people and are about 38m². Each cabin has one double bedroom with an additional single bunk above, plus a single sofa bed in the living room. There is also one bathroom WC with wet room style shower and a drying closet. These cabins are semi-detached and sit side by side, located about 1000 metres from the Ylläsrinne Hotel.</p>
<p><img src="/media/13091637/kissalan-1-2-838x350.jpg" alt="Kissalan Lapland" data-udi="umb://media/537478ddc70b44c6a3c2f7ea391cc13e" /></p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Villa Lumi 1, 2, 3 &amp; 4 </strong>sleep 1-4 people and are about 50m². These cabins have one small double bedroom in an alcove which is separated from the living room by a curtain, and a mezzanine with 2 single beds. Each cabin has one bathroom WC.<strong> </strong>Cabin 3 is semi-detached and cabin 2 is adjacent, both are located about 600 metres from the Ylläsrinne Hotel.</p>
<p>3<img src="/media/13091639/lumi-838x350jpg.jpg" alt="Lumi Cabin Lapland" data-udi="umb://media/a8609c88a8e24dc5b7a5615aa34c0228" /></p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Karpalo </strong>sleeps 2-5 people and is about 44m². This cabin has one twin bedroom, plus one single and one double bed on the mezzanine. There is one bathroom WC with shower.<strong> </strong>This cabin is semi detached and located 500 metres from the Ylläsrinne Hotel.</p>
<p><img src="/media/13091640/karpalo-838x350.jpg" alt="Karpalo Cabin Lapland" data-udi="umb://media/f3905eaf1a064ab99bc24a1e2859055c" /></p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Villa Ylläs A </strong><strong>&amp; B </strong>sleep 2-6 people and are about 55m². Villa Ylläs A has two twin bedrooms, Villa Ylläs B has one double bedroom and one twin bedroom and both cabins have two single beds in the mezzanine (suitable for children aged 8-14 years only). There is one bathroom WC with shower.<strong> </strong>These cabins are semi-detached and sit side by side, located about 500 metres from the Ylläsrinne Hotel.</p>
<p><img src="/media/13091641/suppapolku-838x350.jpg" alt="Suppapolku Cabin Lapland" data-udi="umb://media/44abdf229a064ef381693cd8e5ad0128" /></p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Hotellintie 2B (Mökkelö) </strong>sleeps 2-6 people and is about 55m². This cabin has one double bedroom and one twin bedroom plus 2 single beds in the mezzanine (suitable for children aged 8-14 years only). There is one bathroom WC with a shower.<strong> </strong>This cabin is semi-detached and located about 300 metres from the Ylläsrinne Hotel.</p>
<p><img src="/media/13091642/lintie-838x350.jpg" alt="Lintie Cabin Lapland" data-udi="umb://media/f03d7e14ea424dd4b74bda6437550e60" /></p>
<p><strong>Aukun Maja </strong>sleeps 4-10 people and is 147m². This cabin has three double bedrooms, all with single bunk above and single sofa bed in the living room. There is a large living room on the ground floor with dining area. Upstairs there is another large dining area and kitchen, a separate WC and one bathroom WC with a shower and a drying closet. This cabin is detached and is about 1000 metres from the Ylläsrinne Hotel. </p>
<p><img src="/media/13091646/aukun-maja-838x350jpg.jpg" alt="Aukun Maja Lapland" data-udi="umb://media/161f562f00384224a48c7c52e14a21b7" /></p>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
